 69	 * The boundary types below reproduce the shape the routes/components already
 70	 * consume verbatim (`title`, the misnamed-but-rendered `theme` accent colour,
 71	 * `hero.image.{desktop,mobile}`, `hero.alt`, `[start, end]` ms `dates`, optional
 72	 * ms `registration`, `speakers[].img`, …) so migrating the loaders is a
 73	 * one-line swap and the rendered HTML is byte-for-byte the same.
